# Kerabat Kopi Tiam POS Monorepo Setup

This plan outlines the steps to create a monorepo containing a React-based POS application for Kerabat Kopi Tiam, based on the provided HTML design.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component Name] Monorepo Structure

#### [NEW] [package.json](file:///C:/Users/kompu/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/kerabat-kopi-tiam/package.json)
Root configuration for npm workspaces.
#### [NEW] [apps/pos](file:///C:/Users/kompu/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/kerabat-kopi-tiam/apps/pos)
